  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:10px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4244031830238727\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"754\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/m1eibvmmT3sibGBV9uOEncBGMUPx1C3m5y2mFpkS4200FUajNdsSTbgTOHUDUOSeUict2NfpdfJ5MNFcAOUicPSKVtuZu3F5paHYmCiciax8S3libs/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"558\" data-cropsely2=\"237\" data-imgfileid=\"100013203\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0190a95&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fm1eibvmmT3sibGBV9uOEncBGMUPx1C3m5y2mFpkS4200FUajNdsSTbgTOHUDUOSeUict2NfpdfJ5MNFcAOUicPSKVtuZu3F5paHYmCiciax8S3libs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">嗨大家好！我是阿真！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近尝试了 LibTV ，它是 LiblibAI 推出的专业创作平台，在网页端，它以节点式工作流的形式进行创作，此外，它也可以直接调用 API ，让 Agent 自动生成视频。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上链接👉&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.liblib.tv/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liblib.tv/</a></span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.937037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3b45577&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fm1eibvmmT3s8lKAnsEsE930ibXBMibK5Y6jaQwYpOeJSLEMJiaPF8xlhDg3Kicg1zRkCMqyAN9AkOlp82hBXGxEDtr2dV9eX9RQM785jcQL7ZSZY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以用 Agent（比如龙虾等 Personal Agent）去轻松完成一些视频任务，人可以做的事情，也可以让 Agent 去学去做。不用自己一步步操作，只需要告诉 Agent 我的需求，Agent 直接调用 LibTV 的能力，自动搞定从剧本、分镜、生成到剪辑的整套流程，最后交给我们成片。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">对专业视频创作者来说，它的工作流设计很有帮助；对 Agent 用户来说，它也是一个强大的能力扩展。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border:1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 画布与工具库</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">打开 LibTV，我们可以看到一张可以无限放大缩小的画布。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以在上面自由放置 5 种节点，文本、图片、视频、音频和脚本。所有节点可以拖拽、复制、连线，用连线理清思路。这其中，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2;font-style: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\">尤其是基于图片或者文本去生成脚本的功能，我觉得非常有趣，大家也可以去探索一下。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3685185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22f8831c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s9sbmzmblicUfw82PHamAMua5Cq94PibkycHOc0rpOIKrDwGwQHt8ElKnt7QUnQsmVPxDdovXC7P7XGalKo9O0icLkdYCGicgayib9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32c09c38&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s8hQF2uYRDSmVDxjkgdW8ln6VPPCM2RVUxy9XxTBzxYiadf9alcl2RCcPdXDyPHs79p3ibHuMGOLpT9KZ6YI08PUWocibKr4icicsuo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论是角色设定文本，或是生成的角色三视图和场景图，以及根据这些生成的视频片段，全局旁白脚本和配乐等等全都可以放在画布中。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.762962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78a5b774&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s9btSyO5Kk3Fdzw03vk15y2qm72iaic4P55bRa02Lzibj9XZbk9o5ABrCCcJmaf11yXZKYiaGpMFLaEtGAYGAUY6nfG43Q1nJ6bYso%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"2\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5afcde84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s9bOibpBscialKQ00x5ANwJtzuBwp6r4TjUpEOnK5ARTZ3pSn84JZ5Jgp0xPibI1VPBUTekAzsPW46rxZF2G7q3icGicnc3gv5biaWIY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"2\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3fd55238&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3sicTBYoXVbCmbiad7bjA16Lw6UCCicoTdUn4bjtwibnTA0N5YHyN2Hf6qiaChq6GSlYtv9U1pV8hLxV2pcCBVbnd0Bm82BjhwrFHZVc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于角色图片就可以直接生成分镜脚本，这个功能很能激发灵感。我这里其实就只有上面两张图，根本没有想故事怎么发展，让它帮我写了脚本，直接生成分镜，再组成了视频👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9037037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb0ac9a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s9n5FupklH2PpWho072q9hKwBlVXIHSDvxsBuCp2zf2FAOFLwr3WkHZpulqPAZ2YnPDicn5enK1icibbn3urtCEqA6xN4JHGvdwws%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5175925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cc447558&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s9LT2eic5h60ETrVvSvowtMIPBnO6Yawib8hg3iaKkYLctJ2mOosrYiciabZazN2JJfN1T3Gy0icVNR9bvibc8Qibf8HCqNdfAg27C1r0U%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">看看视频效果，这个没什么逻辑，分镜到提示词全部都是它自行完成👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上面的视频整个过程不到一小时就做完了，要做得精细且维持场景一致效果建议还是角色场景都拆开做多角度然后生成分镜图。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">LibTV 内置了很多专业创作工具。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2;font-style: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\">多宫格分镜生成、连贯分镜、光影校正、剧情推演、多机位镜头设计、角色三视图、画面时间推演</span><span leaf=\"\">等等，这些都是点击斜杠就能调出来的预制魔法，非常高效和高质量。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8351851851851851\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a8911194&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s9dlgYSGajtdLeMRWJNS3aTuQNu4RBeoKBfSlEEAG6Mz79I7KTqs2MMA29F0VyEETzxDrLYeI8JBZibxkXW8voy1Ajb91ZOAVOM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如多机位九宫格用在场景设计上就很方便👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb780e5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s8cUCQJJbGMFNqguPdiaNrstU5RU2Tovp36Sibq6Uu8T1SAcJjJyof1afib8w7HT2rficwjvmyPPHqtMFSzkBt9ia11FYVgB37KntLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3f071f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fm1eibvmmT3s8pJyAtEcCdKrUW5ibkTgCLZJ7AHrAh7Aia9axLzUpelDZwezGjfprSeX7Ob8Qg0LtCLBKbq7wAn1iam9CEQicKKiagSwqdGKy9IbFY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也让创作者从繁琐的重复工作中解放出来，把更多精力放在审美判断和故事思考上。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果是电商营销相关视频，搭好了一条流程后，可以作为工作流，保存成模板反复使用。做系列内容的团队，只需要换个输入素材，整套流程就能按既定风格生产下一期，大幅降低重复工作成本。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border:1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. Agent 加持</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果我们在用龙虾等 Personal Agent，也很有意思。LibTV 开放了 Skill 接口，Agent 可以直接在 IM 里调用。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">只需要将 Skill 安装到我们的工作区：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/libtv-labs/libtv-skills\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/libtv-labs/libtv-skills</a></span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;w